    "title_en": "Central multiplicity distributions in the multi-channel eikonal model",
    "abstract_en": "The multiplicity distribution of charged particles produced in the central rapidity region ($|η|<2.5$) is calculated within the multi-channel eikonal model using the AGK cutting rules and compared with ATLAS data at $\\sqrt{s}=7$ and 13 TeV. The effects of color reconnection and/or string percolation are discussed.",
